#MentalHealth #SDGs I feel greatly fulfilled to have facilitate workshop on root causes of mental health to Yaba artisan association.
#MentalHealth #SDGs Artisans form a significant well organized social networks in Nigeria. Engaging them to understand mental health is key
#MentalHealth #SDGs With today's interaction with the artisans, it is obvious that public health education in communities needs improvement
#MentalHealth #SDGs The artisans were taught about how mental health issues can be detected in their wards right from young age.
#MentalHealth #SDGs Primary health delivery cannot be complete without engaging the organized informal sector like artisan associations
#MentalHealth #SDGs So many disease situation like HIV, mental problems in communities can be prevented if artisans are engaged
#MentalHealth #SDGs If SDG 3 ill be achieved in Nigeria, then we have to properly engage the organized informal sector, leave no one behind
#MentalHealth #SDGs Many of the participants asked a lot of questions on where to go, knowledge about access to mental health is also key
#MentalHealth #SDGs Policy makers have to map out how to communicate SDGs among the artisans and other informal networks to record success
#MentalHealth #SDGs I am happy to be redefining public health through community relations. Engaging informal networks is my passion
